#

Tuna Melt Toast

20 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

FishDairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Quick MealComfort FoodEasy Recipe

Description

A delightful combination of creamy tuna salad and melted cheese on crispy toast, perfect for a quick lunch or snack!

Ingredients

  • canned tuna: 1 can (5 oz)
  • mayonnaise: 2 tablespoons
  • celery, diced: 1/4 cup
  • red onion, diced: 1 tablespoon
  • cheddar cheese, shredded: 1/2 cup
  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • butter: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
